<emphasis box="[281,518,1268,1290]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="386">Pempheris rhomboidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, BPBM 18425, 123 mm SL, Gulf of Aqaba (J.E. Randall).
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption box="[151,1061,2012,2035]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/230622/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="386" targetBox="[241,1335,1332,1996]" targetPageId="9">
